{"word":"δαπανηρός","slug":"δαπανηρός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>δαπανηρός</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:δαπανάω'><el>δαπανάω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b>of men, <i>lavish, extravagant</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>of things, <i>expensive</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b>:—<a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-ρῶς</el>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}